

###############################################

python-movie-catalog-generator

Python script that scans a given movie directory and generates html summary page using IMDB.com information. 

REQUIRMENTS:
- Linux or Mac OS
- Python 2.7 
- Active Internet connection 
- Each of the movie files needs to be stored in a separate directory / folder
- Name of the directories needs follows this pattern: "Name Of The Movie (Year)" For example: "American Hustle (2013)"


USAGE:
- Run python main.py
- Follow instructions from the screen

